Midnight Countdown ⏳🌙

A simple **Python desktop app** built with [CustomTkinter](https://github.com/TomSchimansky/CustomTkinter) that shows a **live countdown to midnight**.
It updates every second and displays the remaining hours, minutes, and seconds until the next day begins.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🕒 Real-time countdown to midnight
* 🎨 Modern dark theme with a green accent (CustomTkinter)
* 📐 Centered, fixed-size window for a clean UI
* 🔄 Updates automatically every second

---

## 📦 Requirements

* Python **3.10+** recommended
* [CustomTkinter](https://github.com/TomSchimansky/CustomTkinter)

Install dependencies with:

```bash
pip install customtkinter
```

> On **Linux**, you may also need to install `python3-tk`:

```bash
sudo apt install python3-tk
```

---

## 🚀 Usage

1. Clone this repo or copy the script into a file, e.g. `midnight_countdown.py`
2. Run the app:

```bash
python3 midnight_countdown.py
```

3. A window will appear with a live countdown timer until midnight.

